Print of Main Street in Davidson NC by Michael Joe Moore










Product Details:
This print is reproduced from the original watercolor by Michael Joe Moore.  It shows a view of Main Street just across from Davidson College.
It would make a great gift for any student at Davidson College or anyone who loves Davidson.
The image is 8 x 10 and is matted in an acid free 11 x 14 matte and placed into a clear plastic sleeve.
It will be shipped to you within five days of recieving your payment by paypal.
To see more of my art got to http://watercolorsmjm.com
